g rewards. Less positively, the recent comments of the departing CEO on the longer term prospects for China were unsettling, whilst of course the change at the helm will provide some caution in regards to continuity. In addition, the company’s very existence is one at the mercy of fashion, and there are no signs that the fierceness of competition is about to subside.</p> </blockquote> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/jamestitcomb/statuses/390012101504143360\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Apple announcement on Ahrendts: <a href=\"http://t.co/nDjItDvBVG\">http://t.co/nDjItDvBVG</a> Tim Cook: &quot;She has shown herself to be an extraordinary leader throughout her career&quot;</p>— James Titcomb (@jamestitcomb) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jamestitcomb/statuses/390012101504143360\">October 15, 2013</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/GarryWhite/statuses/390016605930803200\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Angela Ahrendts shows how to bounce back from a profit warning... But the number of women FTSE CEOs will fall to just two...</p>— Garry White (@GarryWhite) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GarryWhite/statuses/390016605930803200\">October 15, 2013</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2013-10-15T08:45:30.005+01:00\">at 8.45am BST</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-525ceddee4b06d1ee5711922\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2013-10-15T08:25:25.213+01:00\">8.25am <span class=\"timezone\">BST</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/Accendo_Mike/statuses/390013483556691968\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Does Angela realise Apple doesn't sell the same type of Macs?</p>— Mike van Dulken (@Accendo_Mike) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Accendo_Mike